{"tid":682445,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Cyberpunk2077 宣傳費用將高於Witcher 3 並成為規模最大的營銷活動","createTime":"2018-05-29T01:22:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-29T01:41:54.000Z","uid":72478,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"52ec9cdb011674c8bf13a4b9efa9cbe20c597bf0","tid":682445,"uid":72478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T01:22:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/dDPxzv1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdDPxzv1.jpg&h=216d01d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由《The Witcher3：狂獵（The Witcher 3: Wild Hunt）》開發商CD Projekt Red製作的開放世界射擊遊戲《賽博朋克2077（Cyberpunk 2077）》今天終於又公佈出了一些新消息。<br />\n<br />\n在公司最近的財政電話會議上，CDPR向投資者們表示《賽博朋克2077》的營銷活動絕不會&ldquo;一閃而過&rdquo;，而是會成為其目前為止規模最大的營銷活動。<br />\n<br />\nCDPR CEO Adam Kicinski表示公司對於《賽博朋克2077》的期望很高，因此本作的營銷活動&ldquo;會比《The Witcher3》的活動花費更多資金&rdquo;。不過Kicinski也提到，現在就想確定營銷活動的細節還為時尚早，隨著遊戲離公佈日期越來越近，公司對活動的計劃也會越來越詳細。<br />\n<br />\n今年E3展將至，開發商CEO所說的&ldquo;遊戲離公佈日期越來越近&rdquo;無疑讓移植期待本作亮相E3展的粉絲們看到了一絲希望，希望屆時我們能見到這款備受矚目的大作。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲簡介：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Ts6DGvsv4Ds\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTs6DGvsv4Ds&d=Am5SbhvUSQ1Wlx40sPgUt%2BPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=8b3dc276\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Ts6DGvsv4Ds</a>"},{"pid":"50b60297075ff652c05e16546a2ad7010f1dfde0","tid":682445,"uid":41705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T01:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad5fb365935832fb6306f508f9ca7a0c713a0a0","tid":682445,"uid":19013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-29T01:41:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}